    "text": "So, this year, I'm gonna do the whole city."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 31.364,
    "endTime": 34.075,
    "text": "You know, I knew a girl in high school who did that."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 34.3,
    "endTime": 36.119,
    "text": "- She was very popular.   - Ha."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 36.5,
    "endTime": 39.7,
    "text": "Uh, so, Pheebs, uh, where are you doing all your bell ringing?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 40.0,
    "endTime": 42.667,
    "text": "They gave me a great spot right by Macy's."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 42.751,
    "endTime": 49.5,
